description: Describes an Amazon SageMaker Model Card export job.

parameters.name: ModelCardExportJobArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card export job to describe.

nested_items.name: ModelCardExportJobName
nested_items.description: The name of the model card export job to describe.

nested_items.name: ModelCardExportJobArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card export job.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The completion status of the model card export job.
InProgress: The model card export job is in progress.
Completed: The model card export job is complete.
Failed: The model card export job failed. To see the reason for the failure, see the FailureReason field in the response to a DescribeModelCardExportJob call.

nested_items.name: ModelCardName
nested_items.description: The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card that the model export job exports.

nested_items.name: ModelCardVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the model card that the model export job exports.

nested_items.name: OutputConfig
nested_items.description: The export output details for the model card.

nested_items.name: S3OutputPath
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 output path to export your model card PDF.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the model export job was created.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the model export job was last modified.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: The failure reason if the model export job fails.

nested_items.name: S3ExportArtifacts
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 URI of the exported model artifacts.
